    "These findings provide valuable insights that support the potential applications of generative AI in content generation and questionnaire design.",
    "13 found AI chatbots positively influence emotions in business and retail, using a video-based experiment and subjective user questionnaires.",
    "In contrast, our study focuses on academia, using ChatGPT and a more objective emotional detection model to evaluate participants' emotions and feedback while completing various agent-generated questionnaires.",
    "To obtain a more comprehensive knowledge of the impact of AI-powered language models on individuals' emotional and behavioural responses while completing questionnaires, we utilized the third version of the questionnaire (V3).",
